<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 28 Feb 2026 12:22:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国和以色列袭击伊朗后比特币跌破 64,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-28/bitcoin-slides-below-64-000-after-explosions-reported-in-tehran-mm60ajtz</link><description>在美国和以色列周六开始袭击伊朗各地的目标后，比特币和其他加密货币大幅下跌，引发高风险资产波动。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/idqJtRSUh1hc/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Feb 2026 07:35:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-28/bitcoin-slides-below-64-000-after-explosions-reported-in-tehran-mm60ajtz</guid></item><item><title>由于人工智能担心扰乱市场，比特币跌至 65,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-27/bitcoin-sinks-towards-65-000-as-inflation-douses-risk-appetite</link><description>周五，由于投资者担心持续通胀、人工智能干扰以及与私人信贷相关的问题，投资者纷纷撤离风险较高的资产，比特币跌回 65,000 美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iXz9PcgQVV8M/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 15:17:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-27/bitcoin-sinks-towards-65-000-as-inflation-douses-risk-appetite</guid></item><item><title>在线经纪商 XTB 表示波兰的加密货币僵局有扩大的风险</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-27/online-broker-xtb-says-poland-s-crypto-gridlock-risks-expansion</link><description>快速增长的交易平台 XTB SA 表示，其扩张计划面临波兰监管加密资产政治僵局的风险。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWkvQEPhSiqg/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 13:05:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-27/online-broker-xtb-says-poland-s-crypto-gridlock-risks-expansion</guid></item><item><title>英国赌博监管机构将考虑允许投注者使用加密货币支付</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-27/uk-gambling-watchdog-to-weigh-allowing-punters-to-pay-in-crypto</link><description>随着英国逐步采用数字资产法规，英国赌博委员会计划探索允许赌徒用加密货币支付赌注。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/isPu3Z9WkJ9g/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 11:16:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-27/uk-gambling-watchdog-to-weigh-allowing-punters-to-pay-in-crypto</guid></item><item><title>联邦银行监管机构采取行动限制美国稳定币奖励</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-26/federal-bank-regulator-moves-to-restrict-us-stablecoin-rewards</link><description>美国货币监理署提出规则，限制公司通过白标平台推出品牌稳定币并提供与之相关的奖励，这是该机构为实施唐纳德·特朗普总统于 7 月签署的联邦加密货币法的首次重大尝试。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iF__U9SRvdHk/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Feb 2026 22:46:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-26/federal-bank-regulator-moves-to-restrict-us-stablecoin-rewards</guid></item><item><title>如果市场结构法案通过，摩根大通预计加密货币将得到提振</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-26/jpmorgan-sees-crypto-boost-if-market-structure-bill-passes</link><description>摩根大通表示，如果美国立法者在年中之前批准全面的市场结构立法，那么加密货币市场可能会在今年下半年得到有意义的提振，尽管市场情绪仍然不佳。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i0lBCL2gxClo/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Feb 2026 22:21:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-26/jpmorgan-sees-crypto-boost-if-market-structure-bill-passes</guid></item><item><title>MARA与喜达屋合作开发人工智能数据中心</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-26/bitcoin-miner-mara-starwood-partner-to-develop-ai-data-centers</link><description>MARA Holdings Inc. 正在与巴里·斯特恩利希特 (Barry Sternlicht) 的喜达屋资本集团 (Starwood Capital Group) 合作，将比特币矿商的一些现有站点开发为可支持人工智能应用程序和其他一些云服务的基础设施。 MARA 的股价在盘后交易中上涨了 15% 左右。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/izMZw5nO9mNE/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Feb 2026 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-26/bitcoin-miner-mara-starwood-partner-to-develop-ai-data-centers</guid></item><item><title>简街面临加密原住民护理旧伤的愤怒</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-02-26/jane-street-faces-the-wrath-of-crypto-natives-nursing-old-wounds</link><description>瑞安·威克斯 (Ryan Weeks) 撰写了有关加密货币原住民与华尔街之间不稳定关系的文章。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ifkaFEVXZQlg/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Feb 2026 22:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-02-26/jane-street-faces-the-wrath-of-crypto-natives-nursing-old-wounds</guid></item><item><title>风险偏好快速回落后，比特币恢复下滑</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-26/bitcoin-resumes-slide-after-quick-pullback-in-risk-appetite</link><description>比特币周四走低，一天前加密货币的意外上涨引发了投资者的乐观情绪，他们认为数字资产市场在经历了四个多月的下滑后即将触底。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iBcgLaWQAhRY/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Feb 2026 17:42:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-26/bitcoin-resumes-slide-after-quick-pullback-in-risk-appetite</guid></item><item><title>与特朗普挂钩的比特币矿工因加密货币崩溃而遭受重创</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-26/bitcoin-miner-tied-to-trump-family-pummeled-by-crypto-crash</link><description>美国比特币公司（American Bitcoin Corp.）是特朗普家族支持的矿商，乘着加密货币的热潮在纳斯达克首次亮相时表现出色，但现在却陷入了该行业自 2022 年以来最严重的溃败之中。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i4BHJ71PRv94/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Feb 2026 11:49:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-26/bitcoin-miner-tied-to-trump-family-pummeled-by-crypto-crash</guid></item></channel></rss>